T02D1773:268b-1: shr'i ma h'a k'a la s+y'a shta pa da sto tra n'a ma /
T02D1773:268b-3: dpal nag po chen po'i bstod pa rkang pa brgyad pa zhes bya ba /
T02D1773:268b-4: dpal nag po chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1773:268b-5: aom grub par gyur cig / h'um h'um phat ces
T02D1773:268b-6: drag po'i sgra yis srid pa gsum gyi khongs ni
T02D1773:268b-8: ha ha ta ta zhes brjod gang zhig dus kun du ni bdud sde shin tu 'jigs mdzad cing //
T02D1773:268b-9: kam kam kam zhes thod pa'i phreng bas dbu la sbras shing nag po'i mchu dang mtshungs pa'i sku //
T02D1773:268b-10: brum brum brum zhes khros pa'i mchog gi khro gnyer 'jigs mdzad 'jigs pa kha gdangs sha za zhing //
T02D1773:268b-11: dbu skra dang ni sma ra ches ser nye bar spyod pa'i zhing skyong khyod kyis srung bar mdzod //
T02D1773:268b-12: ram ram ram zhes spyan dmar 'khyug cing bsgyur mdzad krum krum krum zhes rab sgrogs spyan gyis gzigs //
T02D1773:268b-13: smin ma ser zhing mche gtsigs ro yi gdan la dgyes pa'i zhing skyong khyod kyis zhing skyong mdzod //
T02D1773:268b-14: ha ha h'um dang k'i li k'i li zhes sgrogs phyag g-yon kha tv'am gar bcas thod pa bsnams //
T02D1773:268b-15: ru ru ru zhes khrag gi rgyun 'bab phyag gis bsnams shing gsol ba 'thung ba la dgyes shing //
T02D1773:268b-16: kham kham kham zhes gtum mo'i phyag g-yas gri gug ral gri bgegs rnams la ni rol mdzad pas //
T02D1773:268b-17: dam dam dam zhes da ma ru can 'di yis 'dul mdzad 'khor bcas zhing skyong khyod kyis srungs //
T02D1773:268b-18: rab tu rngam zhing mgo bo rnams kyi phreng bas gshin rje dang mtshungs 'jigs pa'i sku brgyan cing //
T02D1773:268b-19: ksham ksham ksham zhes bzod pa'i shugs can ca co sgrogs par byed pa'i gdug pa rnams bzung ste //
T02D1773:268b-20: gcig pus sna tshogs mnan nas ka ka ha ha
T02D1773:268b-21: brjod mdzad char sprin sngon po lta bu'i mdog /
T02D1773:268b-22: sku la mi yi sha dang rgyu mas brel pa'i
T02D1773:268b-23: rgyan gyis kun nas brgyan cing zhal du gsol //
T02D1773:268b-24: drag shul phyag gis 'dod pa'i gzugs dang mi sdug gzugs can gyi ni 'byung po ro langs tshogs //
T02D1773:268b-25: ma lus bzung nas myur du bsad pa rnams kyi mgo bo'i khrag rgyun 'bab pa rab tu gsol //
T02D1773:268b-26: hr'im kshui shr'i zhes sngags kyi gsungs can pa tsa pa tsa'i sngags kyis bgegs rnams rab tu bsregs //
T02D1773:269a-1: rol pa sel zhing mi yis gang ba'i mtsho la zhing skyong khyod kyis bsrung ba mdzad //
T02D1773:269a-2: phem phem phat ces sgrogs pa so sor bskyod pa'i me dpung chen po'i dbus su bzhugs nas su //
T02D1773:269a-3: rigs kyi lus can srung bar mdzad cing sgrub pa rnams kyi zhing rnams nges par zhing skyong mdzod //
T02D1773:269a-4: phyugs rnams kyi ni nyin re bzhin du bgegs dang sdig 'joms dri med brnyes pa chu nyi bzhin //
T02D1773:269a-5: tsam tsam tsam zhes gtum pa'i shugs kyis rab dbye rmad byung 'od kyi 'jig rten snang mdzad pa //
T02D1773:269a-6: kram kram kram zhes gshegs pas dgra bo nyon mongs pa rnams nges par nyon mongs 'joms mdzad cing /
T02D1773:269a-7: sam sam sam zhes tshogs pa'i bdag nyid dam tshig thos 'dzin zhing skyong gang yin khyod kyis skyongs //
T02D1773:269a-8: bam bam bam zhes gshin rje ltar 'gro dri ma med pa'i sna tshogs chu bzhin gzigs mdzad cing //
T02D1773:269a-9: yam yam yam zhes rlung gi shugs kyis myur du rgyu zhing nyon mongs 'jig rten gnod byed mkhyen //
T02D1773:269a-10: klim klim klim zhes gdug pa'i gzugs kyis srid gsum nyin mtshan dus kun nyon mongs gyur pa gang //
T02D1773:269a-11: pam pam pam zhes thugs rje'i zhags pas byol song rnams 'dzin phyag gis gdul bya rnams skyong la //
T02D1773:269a-12: sngags bdag sngags kyi lus can thugs kyi sngags pa rnams la 'bras bu blo gros mtshungs med ster //
T02D1773:269a-13: zhing rnams skyong bar mdzad pa khyod kyis 'gro ba'i lus rnams ma lus yun ring skyong du gsol //
T02D1773:269a-14: sgrub pa po'am slob dpon 'ga' zhig thos 'dzin gang zhig blo ldan nus pa dang //
T02D1773:269a-15: thun gsum du ni sngags rnams brgyad po klog byed de ni bsod nams ldan par 'gyur ba dang //
T02D1773:269a-16: tshe dang dpal dang grags dang 'byor ba 'dzin dang gzi rgyas pa dang mtshungs med dang //
T02D1773:269a-17: sa stengs dang na mtho ris su'ang de yi bgegs kyi tshogs rnams rtag tu nyams par 'gyur //
T02D1773:269a-18: dpal nag po chen po la bstod pa rkang pa brgyad pa zhes bya ba //
